---
/*
  On-brand teaching diagram for /pipeda-data-destruction. Ties the legal
  obligation to the artifact: personal information no longer needed -> verified
  NIST 800-88 wipe -> tamper-evident certificate -> record for your PIA /
  retention policy. Site palette + sans font; responsive inline SVG.
*/
---

<figure class="not-prose my-8">
  <svg
    viewBox="0 0 840 210"
    role="img"
    aria-label="How a verified wipe supports a privacy obligation: when personal information is no longer needed, run a verified NIST 800-88 wipe, which produces a tamper-evident certificate, which becomes the record for your privacy impact assessment or retention policy."
    class="mx-auto block h-auto w-full max-w-3xl rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-2"
    style="font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;"
  >
    <title>Personal information no longer needed, to a verified NIST 800-88 wipe, to a tamper-evident certificate, to a record for your PIA or retention policy</title>

    <!-- Node 1: PI no longer needed -->
    <g>
      <rect x="16" y="30" width="188" height="150" rx="14" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#E4E8EE" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <rect x="80" y="54" width="60" height="46" rx="6" fill="#F4F6F9" stroke="#5A6472" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <line x1="90" y1="66" x2="130" y2="66" stroke="#5A6472" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <line x1="90" y1="76" x2="130" y2="76" stroke="#5A6472" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <line x1="90" y1="86" x2="118" y2="86" stroke="#5A6472" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <circle cx="136" cy="96" r="12" fill="#B42318" />
      <path d="M131 91 l10 10 M141 91 l-10 10" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2.1" stroke-linecap="round" />
      <text x="110" y="138" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#141922">Personal info</text>
      <text x="110" y="156" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11.5" fill="#5A6472">no longer needed</text>
    </g>

    <!-- Node 2: verified wipe -->
    <g>
      <rect x="234" y="30" width="188" height="150" rx="14" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#E4E8EE" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <rect x="292" y="52" width="72" height="44" rx="6" fill="#EAF1FF" stroke="#3E7BFA" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <path d="M316 66 a13 13 0 1 1 -8 4" fill="none" stroke="#3E7BFA" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" />
      <path d="M305 68 l3 -8 l7 5 z" fill="#3E7BFA" />
      <text x="328" y="136" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#141922">Verified</text>
      <text x="328" y="154" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11.5" fill="#5A6472">NIST 800-88 wipe</text>
    </g>

    <!-- Node 3: certificate -->
    <g>
      <rect x="452" y="30" width="188" height="150" rx="14" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#E4E8EE" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <rect x="512" y="52" width="58" height="50" rx="5" fill="#F4F6F9" stroke="#5A6472" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <line x1="522" y1="64" x2="560" y2="64" stroke="#5A6472" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <line x1="522" y1="74" x2="560" y2="74" stroke="#5A6472" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <line x1="522" y1="84" x2="548" y2="84" stroke="#5A6472" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <circle cx="566" cy="96" r="12" fill="#158048" />
      <path d="M560 96 l4 4 l7 -9" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
      <text x="546" y="138" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#141922">Tamper-evident</text>
      <text x="546" y="156" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11.5" fill="#5A6472">certificate</text>
    </g>

    <!-- Node 4: record for PIA -->
    <g>
      <rect x="670" y="30" width="154" height="150" rx="14" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#E4E8EE" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <rect x="726" y="52" width="42" height="52" rx="4" fill="#EAF1FF" stroke="#3E7BFA" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <rect x="736" y="46" width="22" height="10" rx="3" fill="#3E7BFA" />
      <line x1="734" y1="70" x2="760" y2="70" stroke="#3E7BFA" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <line x1="734" y1="80" x2="760" y2="80" stroke="#3E7BFA" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <line x1="734" y1="90" x2="752" y2="90" stroke="#3E7BFA" stroke-width="1.3" />
      <text x="747" y="138" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#141922">Record for your</text>
      <text x="747" y="156" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11.5" fill="#5A6472">PIA / retention</text>
    </g>

    <!-- arrows -->
    <g fill="#3E7BFA">
      <path d="M212 98 l14 7 l-14 7 z" />
      <path d="M430 98 l14 7 l-14 7 z" />
      <path d="M648 98 l14 7 l-14 7 z" />
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="mt-3 text-center text-sm text-muted">
    A verified wipe turns a retention obligation into a per-drive record you can put in a PIA or
    retention policy.
  </figcaption>
</figure>
